high_descs: Turn left and circle around the corner of the table and face the table.
Pick the knife up off of the table.
Turn around away from the table and walk towards the counter with the toaster.
Slice the loaf of bread between the toaster and sink.
Take a step to the left and face the counter again.
Place the knife of the counter to the left of the apple.
Step back over to face the loaf of bread.
Take a middle slice of bread.
Turn around, take a step out and then turn left towards the refrigerator and walk to it.
Open the door, place the slice of bread inside, close the door to chill the bread for a moment. And finally remove the slice once more closing the door behind.
Turn around to face the opposite direction and walk all the way to the oven. Make your way around the oven to you left until you face the green waste basket next to the oven.
Put the slice of bread in the waste basket.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of bread in the waste basket.

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the end of the table where the green sponge will be on the left.
Pick up the knife closest to you.
Turn around and walk to the counter with the apple and bread on it.
Slice half of the loaf of bread.
Move left to stand in front of the apple.
Place the knife on the counter to the immediate left of the apple.
Move to your right to stand in front of the loaf of bread.
Pick up the center slice of bread.
Turn and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and place the bread in the gray bin directly above the crisper drawers, close the fridge door; allow to cool, open the fridge door, pick up the slice of bread, close the door.
Turn and walk to the green bin to the left of the stove.
Place the bread slice in the green bin.
anns.task_desc: Slice a loaf of bread, chill a slice, place it in the green bin

high_descs: move forward towards the table
pick up the knife
turn around towards the table
slice the bread on the table
turn left of the table
drop the knife  on the table
move right to the slices
pick up a slice
turn right towards the fridge
place the slice to cool and then take it out
turn around to the trash can
trash the slice of bread
anns.task_desc: drop a cold slice of bread in the bin
